{"tid":1393093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】我正式宣佈全民派傳單軍隊全面進場！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T08:34:01.000Z","uid":269153,"like":111,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4909a3ccff0ecd8f01564f84bc5548cba7f1e925","tid":1393093,"uid":269153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:30:16.000Z","msg":"聽日8月2日就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民帶「八五罷工」白手帶</span></span></strong> ，今日同手足講呢單野佢好似仲未知咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sV5LjkE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsV5LjkE.jpg&h=4389479f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ReTdtfM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FReTdtfM.jpg&h=3d345c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>見到有學生自發網上叫人今日同聽日自發罷街站派傳單派白手帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n銀髮族都有呼籲</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZN0fGAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZN0fGAZ.jpg&h=3ac8b629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喂，我地一定要搞到全民街站！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>自己印定leaflet同埋帶定白手帶，返工又派下，放工又派下！！！！食飯又派下！！！排隊去廁所又派下</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要全香港人都知8.2白手帶日同繼續呼籲八五罷工！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7RCawx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7RCawx.jpg&h=3be6fa17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【85罷工資源包】  (乜撚野都有，罷工須知同傳單）<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/85StrikeResources\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F85StrikeResources&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl55uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=0ae5a13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/85StrikeResources</a><br />\n和理非終極升級反送中TG Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/unionsforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FunionsforHK&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl55uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=499b12c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/unionsforHK</a><br />\n反送中 文宣谷 Channel:warning: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/l